{
  "stem": "1222.3",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 52,
      "text": "If they will think that I should get killed-- and I will tell you the truth.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 53,
      "text": "If it means to die, and if it means [INAUDIBLE], I don't know if somebody [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 54,
      "text": "I wouldn't mind if I get killed there.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 55,
      "text": "It doesn't bother me.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 56,
      "text": "It doesn't bother me.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 57,
      "text": "I have a nice memory, and it will be passed around through the generation.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 58,
      "text": "I got two wonderful children, you know.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 59,
      "text": "And that's life has got to go on.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The message why I'm talking all this thing, because I feel like that if anyone-- just like you asked yourself-- do you want to be buried and forget about you, or you want to be memorized?",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So I feel because you're not living in-- in the states, that we are living here, that doesn't mean they don't have to be memorized.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "That's why I feel we should put in the names.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Doesn't matter.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Wherever it is.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "If it's in Miami.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "We have one in Winnipeg.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "We should put in to memorize.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Like the rabbi said in Winnipeg to one of my cousins-- I asked him to come.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "He says, don't worry.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "He ignores it.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "He wouldn't go even probably to his own parents here to go to put in their headstone.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "You know, he put in the headstone, but he think that's all.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "I believe very highly, when I die, I would appreciate it very, very much if my children will come once in awhile as often as possible to have a look where I'm laying.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That's respect for the dead people.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The people don't-- can't talk.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And why I feel that way too, because I'll give you a good example.",
      "word_count": 14
    }
  ],
